  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Five Unique Heroes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2532770/extras/fe29c7c8d332b398b90669751b0693ba.poster.avif?t=1764263967\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2532770/extras/fe29c7c8d332b398b90669751b0693ba.webm?t=1764263967\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2532770/extras/fe29c7c8d332b398b90669751b0693ba.mp4?t=1764263967\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Guide the heroes of Dragonero in this epic adventure: <strong>Ian, Gmor, Myrva, Alben and Sera</strong>. Join the legends in the fight to save Erondàr. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tackle the <strong>story of each of the characters</strong> before bringing them all together in the main adventure: make your way through the intrigue and dangers that make up the rich and engaging story of the Dragonero universe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Turn-based combat</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2532770/extras/5a534d5da9f9164cde3811cc87f9191a.poster.avif?t=1764263967\" width=600 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2532770/extras/5a534d5da9f9164cde3811cc87f9191a.webm?t=1764263967\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2532770/extras/5a534d5da9f9164cde3811cc87f9191a.mp4?t=1764263967\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the excitement of <strong>turn-based combat</strong> as in the great role-playing game classics. Choose your skills wisely, use unique items, and coordinate your moves to defeat fearsome opponents. Victory depends on your strategy and planning.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Dungeons and battles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2532770/extras/4fc589d54e67fb90f508b3f3b5baf779.poster.avif?t=1764263967\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2532770/extras/4fc589d54e67fb90f508b3f3b5baf779.webm?t=1764263967\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2532770/extras/4fc589d54e67fb90f508b3f3b5baf779.mp4?t=1764263967\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face evil in the form of Draquir, a powerful new threat. As darkness spreads across Erondàr, the fate of the world lies in your hands. Prepare to face breathtaking trials in over ten different settings that will delight any explorer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">A vast openworld: the Erondár</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2532770/extras/09619ea16b9dca9dc77b060587e86db3.poster.avif?t=1764263967\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2532770/extras/09619ea16b9dca9dc77b060587e86db3.webm?t=1764263967\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2532770/extras/09619ea16b9dca9dc77b060587e86db3.mp4?t=1764263967\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in a vast and mysterious world, exploring unknown lands and <strong>both procedurally generated and hand-created dungeons</strong>. Each adventure is unique, with new challenges and treasures to discover with each journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Rest and do not succumb to fatigue</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2532770/extras/b69deb1dd0c90786a1eb24058efc59ea.poster.avif?t=1764263967\" width=600 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2532770/extras/b69deb1dd0c90786a1eb24058efc59ea.webm?t=1764263967\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2532770/extras/b69deb1dd0c90786a1eb24058efc59ea.mp4?t=1764263967\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battles and exploration will fatigue Heroes; manage rests and use items to invigorate them. Face an ever-increasing <strong>challenge</strong> as you venture deeper into Erondàr. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready for a gaming experience that will enchant Dragonero fans and capture the souls of classic RPG lovers. The fate of Erondàr is in your hands - will you be the hero the world needs?</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Five Unique Heroes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2532770/extras/fe29c7c8d332b398b90669751b0693ba.poster.avif?t=1764263967\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2532770/extras/fe29c7c8d332b398b90669751b0693ba.webm?t=1764263967\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2532770/extras/fe29c7c8d332b398b90669751b0693ba.mp4?t=1764263967\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Guide the heroes of Dragonero in this epic adventure: <strong>Ian, Gmor, Myrva, Alben and Sera</strong>. Join the legends in the fight to save Erondàr. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tackle the <strong>story of each of the characters</strong> before bringing them all together in the main adventure: make your way through the intrigue and dangers that make up the rich and engaging story of the Dragonero universe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Turn-based combat</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2532770/extras/5a534d5da9f9164cde3811cc87f9191a.poster.avif?t=1764263967\" width=600 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2532770/extras/5a534d5da9f9164cde3811cc87f9191a.webm?t=1764263967\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2532770/extras/5a534d5da9f9164cde3811cc87f9191a.mp4?t=1764263967\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the excitement of <strong>turn-based combat</strong> as in the great role-playing game classics. Choose your skills wisely, use unique items, and coordinate your moves to defeat fearsome opponents. Victory depends on your strategy and planning.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Dungeons and battles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2532770/extras/4fc589d54e67fb90f508b3f3b5baf779.poster.avif?t=1764263967\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2532770/extras/4fc589d54e67fb90f508b3f3b5baf779.webm?t=1764263967\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2532770/extras/4fc589d54e67fb90f508b3f3b5baf779.mp4?t=1764263967\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face evil in the form of Draquir, a powerful new threat. As darkness spreads across Erondàr, the fate of the world lies in your hands. Prepare to face breathtaking trials in over ten different settings that will delight any explorer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">A vast openworld: the Erondár</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2532770/extras/09619ea16b9dca9dc77b060587e86db3.poster.avif?t=1764263967\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2532770/extras/09619ea16b9dca9dc77b060587e86db3.webm?t=1764263967\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2532770/extras/09619ea16b9dca9dc77b060587e86db3.mp4?t=1764263967\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in a vast and mysterious world, exploring unknown lands and <strong>both procedurally generated and hand-created dungeons</strong>. Each adventure is unique, with new challenges and treasures to discover with each journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Rest and do not succumb to fatigue</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2532770/extras/b69deb1dd0c90786a1eb24058efc59ea.poster.avif?t=1764263967\" width=600 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2532770/extras/b69deb1dd0c90786a1eb24058efc59ea.webm?t=1764263967\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2532770/extras/b69deb1dd0c90786a1eb24058efc59ea.mp4?t=1764263967\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battles and exploration will fatigue Heroes; manage rests and use items to invigorate them. Face an ever-increasing <strong>challenge</strong> as you venture deeper into Erondàr. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready for a gaming experience that will enchant Dragonero fans and capture the souls of classic RPG lovers. The fate of Erondàr is in your hands - will you be the hero the world needs?</p>",
